title: Minister Attaf receives the Ambassador of the Socialist Republic of Vietnam in Algiers
text: The Minister of Foreign Affairs and National Community Abroad, Ahmed Attaf, received, Tuesday, the Ambassador of the Socialist Republic of Vietnam, Nguyen Thanh Vinh, who paid him a farewell visit at the end of his mission in Algeria.
The meeting allowed to evaluate the relations of friendship and cooperation between the two countries and to praise the efforts made by the ambassador for their development.
